{"tid":1560593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲失蹤男秀茂坪墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-09-11T09:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T15:20:50.000Z","uid":56452,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f8135fb2a822ed2bfb10fd38efc18114270fac0c","tid":1560593,"uid":56452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"23歲男子朱植雄前日（9日）上午離開秀茂坪秀明道的住所後便告失蹤，其家人同日向警方報案。至今早（11日）11時24分，警方接報，一名男子倒臥於秀茂坪邨秀義樓一天井，救護人員到場證實男子已告不治，現場沒有遺書。警方經調查後，確認死者為朱植雄，相信他從上址天台墮下，事件沒有可疑，其死因仍有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n<br />\n年輕人專線<br />\n<br />\n香港輔導及心理學會：WhatsApp熱線6218 1084 (提供英語及粵語專業輔導服務)<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：青少年生命專線 2382 0777<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會青少年網上輔導平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"https://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=44449535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190911/s00001/1568192243972/23%e6%ad%b2%e5%a4%b1%e8%b9%a4%e7%94%b7%e7%a7%80%e8%8c%82%e5%9d%aa%e5%a2%ae%e6%a8%93%e4%ba%a1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568192243972%2F23%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e8%25b9%25a4%25e7%2594%25b7%25e7%25a7%2580%25e8%258c%2582%25e5%259d%25aa%25e5%25a2%25ae%25e6%25a8%2593%25e4%25ba%25a1&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=c71914b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568192243972%2F23%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e8%25b9%25a4%25e7%2594%25b7%25e7%25a7%2580%25e8%258c%2582%25e5%259d%25aa%25e5%25a2%25ae%25e6%25a8%2593%25e4%25ba%25a1&h=ce938270\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%